        "rich_text_CNg3En": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introducing Lucira Jewelry: Reimagining Diamonds for Modern India",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Introducing Lucira Jewelry: Reimagining Diamonds for Modern India</h2>",
            "custom_id": "introducing"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_aEcqXr": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>This is where Lucira Jewelry enters the story. We believe the question is no longer just where are diamonds found in India, but how can they be sourced responsibly for the modern consumer. We are a design-first brand dedicated to making fine jewelry contemporary, accessible, and deeply personal through the brilliance of lab-grown diamonds.</p>",
