        "rich_text_GXiUjf": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Our Products: We offer a full range of<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-ring\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">engagement ring</span></a>, wedding bands, earrings, necklaces, bracelets, and modern Mangalsutras.</p><p>Exclusive Designs: Explore our unique collections like 'On The Move' and 'Hexa', which embody our philosophy of innovative design.</p><p>Unmatched Brilliance: We have developed five exclusive diamond cuts engineered to maximize light performance and create a sparkle you won't find anywhere else.</p><p>Those looking for timeless romance can discover the perfect<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-for-women\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">engagement ring for women</span></a> that beautifully blends tradition with modern design.</p>",
