          "name": "Personalized Jewelry Design and AI-Led Customization",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Personalized Jewelry Design and AI-Led Customization</h3><p>Why choose an off-the-shelf design when you can create your own? Our bespoke services put you in the designer's seat.</p><ul><li>Share Your Vision: Start with an idea, sketch, or inspiration.<br/></li><li>Co-Create with Experts: Work with our designers and leverage our AI-powered tools and virtual try-ons to visualize your piece.<br/></li><li>Crafted to Perfection: We bring your dream jewelry to life with meticulous attention to detail.</li></ul>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7EdFpY": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Experience the Lucira Difference In-Person and Online",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Experience the Lucira Difference In-Person and Online</h2><p>Whether you prefer to shop from home or desire a hands-on experience, Lucira meets you where you are. We are a digital-first brand with a human touch.</p><p>Connect with Our Experts: Video Calls and Flagship Store Experiences</p><ul><li>Digital Convenience: Browse and shop on our website, get instant help via WhatsApp, and enjoy nationwide delivery.<br/></li><li>Personalized Consultations: Schedule a 'Video Call with a Jewelry Expert' for one-on-one guidance, from diamond education to design advice.<br/></li></ul><p>Future Flagships: We are expanding our physical footprint with flagship stores like the<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/chembur-store\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Chembur Lucira Store</span></a> to offer an even more immersive and personal brand experience.</p>",
